id="post-3390" class="post-3390 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-equality category-freedom tag-gay tag-marriage tag-new-york-city tag-nyc"><h2 class="entry-title"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2012/07/31/in-new-york-city-gay-marriage-is-worth-259-million/" title="Permalink to In New York City Gay Marriage is Worth $259 Million" rel="bookmark">In New York City Gay Marriage is Worth $259 Million</a></h2><div
class="entry-meta"> <span
class="entry-date" title="2012/07/31 10:50 am"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2012/07/31/in-new-york-city-gay-marriage-is-worth-259-million/" title="In New York City Gay Marriage is Worth $259 Million" rel="bookmark">2012/07/31 10:50 am</a></span><span
class="entry-meta-sep"> / </span><span
class="entry-author author vcard"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/author/administrator/" title="by Adam Clare" rel="author">Adam Clare</a></span></div><div
class="entry-content clearfix"><p>You read that correctly, a $259 million (USD) boom in New York City&#8217;s economy is thanks to respecting human rights! Changing the law to reflect reality and letting homosexuals marry one another has generated some needed economic growth for the local economy. All of this in just one year!</p><blockquote><p>&#8220;Marriage equality has made our City more open, inclusive and free &#8212; and it has also helped to create jobs and support our economy,&#8221; Mayor Bloomberg said in a statement.</p><p>More than 8,200 same-sex marriage licenses have been issued over the past year, representing more than 10% of the 75,000 licenses issued in the city, according to a survey conducted by the City Clerk&#8217;s Office and NYC &#038; Company, the city&#8217;s tourism and marketing organization.</p></blockquote><p><a
href="http://money.cnn.com/2012/07/24/pf/gay-marriage-economic-impact/">Read more at CNN.</a></p><div
class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-1111807-3390-5384310e99932' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/#blog_id=1111807&amp;post_id=3390&amp;origin=www.thingsaregood.com&amp;obj_id=1111807-3390-5384310e99932' data-name='like-post-frame-1111807-3390-5384310e99932'><h3 class='sd-title'>Like this:</h3><div
